## சென்னைப் பல்கலைக்கழகத் தமிழ்ப் பேரகராதி
எழுதீவு
--
- eḻutīvu
- n. <</>எழு+.
- The seven continents or divisions of the earth which accg. to Purāṇās are said to exist in the form of concentric circles with the mountain Mēru as their centre, each being surrounded by one of seven ring-shaped seas, viz., நாவலந்தீவு, இறலித்தீவு, இலவந்தீவு
- .